Source Code : https://git.pleroma.social/pleroma/

Pleroma is an open source social media platfrom, like old Twitter.
It currently has 921 instances and 21K active users.
It hosts mostly tech-savvy instances but self hosting a Pleroma instance is easy.

Pros[+]:
-Uses extremely low resources, even can be hosted by a Raspberry Pi, written in Elixir.
-Simple UI and UX.

Cons[-]:
-Most people are tech oriented. It may sound boring if you don't like technology.


